Package: u5mr
Type: Package
Title: Under-Five Child Mortality Estimation  
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Myo Minn",
             family = "Oo",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "dr.myominnoo@gmail.com",
             comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4089-016X")))
Maintainer: Myo Minn Oo <dr.myominnoo@gmail.com>
Description: This is a tool for estimating child mortality. 
    Current implementation includes the Trussell version of the Brass method using 
    the Coale-Demeny model life tables and supporting datasets of coefficients and
    automatic interpolating values between probabilities of dying at a certain age 
    and model tables. 
URL: https://github.com/myominnoo/u5mr
BugReports: https://github.com/myominnoo/u5mr/issues
